BAMBI - Tools for processing BAM files
======================================

This is a small collection of tools for processing BAM files.

The project is a SeqAn sandbox.  See the SeqAn Getting Started tutorial to see
for details on how you can build it:

    http://trac.seqan.de/wiki/Tutorial/GettingStarted

The short version is:

 * Check out SeqAn.
 * Check out this repository into sandbox/bambi.
 * Call CMake for SeqAn.
 * Build the apps in this sandbox.
